cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  This directory vendors a Markdown conversion of the glTF 2.0 Interactivity
  extension specification, published by the Khronos Group. If you use or
  reference this content, please cite the original specification (below),
  not this repository.
type: standard
title: "glTF 2.0 Interactivity Extension Specification"
authors:
  - name: "The Khronos 3D Formats Working Group"
  - name: "The Khronos Group Inc."
repository-code: "https://github.com/KhronosGroup/glTF"
url: "https://registry.khronos.org/glTF/specs/2.0/glTF-2.0.html"
license: "CC-BY-4.0"
commit: 9804322b71b782b797ce63f6787b9a0341cb6b47
date-released: "2026-07-07"
identifiers:
  - type: url
    value: "https://github.com/KhronosGroup/glTF/blob/9804322b71b782b797ce63f6787b9a0341cb6b47/extensions/2.0/Khronos/KHR_interactivity/Specification.adoc"
    description: >-
      Exact source revision converted into this directory's 00-04 Markdown
      files (AsciiDoc -> DocBook via asciidoctor -b docbook5 -> Markdown via
      pandoc -f docbook -t gfm, then split at the six top-level headings:
      Foreword, Introduction, Concepts, Functional Specification [split
      further into 02_node_types.md's "Operations" catalog and
      03_extending_gltf.md from "Extending glTF Object Model" onward], JSON
      Syntax, Validation). To refresh, repeat the same conversion against the
      current interactivity branch and update this file's commit/date.
